Package com.andreamazzon.session6.generics.readstring

Class CharactersOfString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.andreamazzon.session6.generics.readstring.CharactersOfString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericPointer<java.lang.Character>
    public class CharactersOfString
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericPointer<java.lang.Character>
    This class implements the GenericPointer interface, In particular, it implements the method next() with return type Character. The method is used in order to read all the separate characters of a string, when it is called iteratively.
    Author:
    Andrea Mazzon
